snippet.textDisplay:
Looking back to this news of may 2014, from today...Jan-Feb 2020, the Coronavirus, as identified here in 2014 with this MERS, the host being sick camels....what mode of transmission was it that this Corona-virus spread from sick camels to humans in Saudi? I know that Arabs do eat camel meat in various forms. But this documentary does not tell us the mode of spread from animals to humans. Its interesting to see current VP Mike Pence, who was the Governor of Indiana at the time in 2014.
1:40 to 2:10..."CDC and authorities have been able to obtain viruses from these infected camels, compared them to the viruses from sick humans and determine as well as demonstrate the similarities"for a proper containment of the situation. This timing captions are from the original 2014 video of MERS of Saudi Arabia.
Now in 2020, Yuhan China, the epicenter....they have an elaborate plan and in fact China is rapidly building hospital specially designed to deal with the outbreak of the Corona virus of 2020. I sincerely believe that the response China and Chinese authorities have in 2020, is much more transparent as well as on a much grandeur scale than the response given by then(2014) epicenter of Saudi Arabia.
